      "how_far": "Cleared the game (defeated the boss / \u901a\u5173) on the majority of seeds: ~0.59-0.63 win rate across ~450 fresh held-out seeds (MEAN_EVAL ~0.97-1.02), fastest win ~step 18259 (eval ~1.80, full 19.5M boss HP destroyed). Non-wins still reach the boss and chip 10-90% of its HP.",
      "failure_modes": [
        "Early/mid boss-fight deaths at low level: overwhelmed by the dense bullet barrage (300/450-dmg bullets) and pinned in a bottom corner where a descending elite's contact (~2700, near one-shot) finishes a thin HP pool before shields accumulate.",
        "Occasional DPS-timeouts: survived the full 90k steps but upgrade RNG never offered enough DPS (no pierce / low multishot), so the 19.5M-HP boss wasn't finished (reached ~50-90% destroyed).",
        "Extreme chaotic sensitivity: tiny policy changes flip which seeds live/die, so most micro-tuning washes across large seed sets; only a handful of orthogonal/mechanic-exploiting levers gave robust gains."
      ],
      "lessons": [
        "Boss has ~19.5M HP; base autofire (~2.4k DPS) is hopeless. DPS scales 50-100x via pierce (bullets rake the 120px-tall boss for per-tick damage) + multishot + fire-rate + crit + satellites, all gated by leveling.",
        "Auto-fire shoots straight up, so stay x-aligned under the boss (~120px wide) or you deal ~0 damage; dodging off-axis tanks DPS.",
        "Survival is the master key: surviving long enough always wins (out-level + out-DPS the boss). Deaths, not low DPS, dominate failures.",
        "Killing enemies IS defense (fewer enemies => fewer bullets); pure evasion backfires. An INSTANT greedy per-tick dodge (pick the safest reachable resting spot, re-planned every tick) beat rollout/hysteresis/2-ply \u2014 responsiveness > commitment.",
        "Biggest robust gains were orthogonal additions of survival without costing DPS: collect heart (+1000 shield) and levelup (+1 level) pickups; lean upgrades toward survival/exp before the boss so you enter with a buffer.",
        "Exploit states you're ALREADY in, don't chase pickups: during the `invincible` pickup's ~5s immunity, stop dodging and lock under the boss for free max-DPS (validated win-rate gain on held-out). But aggressively DETOURING for invincible/bomb/exp pickups gets you killed en route. Bombs clear the whole screen of bullets on contact \u2014 useful, but only grab them opportunistically.",
        "Validate on large fresh seed sets, not the tuning set: the chaos makes single/small-set results misleading and easy to overfit."
      ],
      "attempts_used": 45
    },
